text:
$LITE EARNINGS CALL AT 5:00 PM ET!

The photonics and optoelectronics play has rallied massively this year, and it posted a double beat for Q3 2026! Ahead of the conference call, here's a look at Lumentum's revenue - and revenue growth - by product type for the quarter.

@tradertvlive $SPY $QQQ @Lumentum

